title: Stanley Cup Final Game 4 Highlights | Panthers vs. Oilers - June 15, 2024
descrip: Connor McDavid scored and notched three assists to set a new playoff record, Dylan Holloway scored twice, and Stuart Skinner made 32 saves to help the Edmonton Oilers crush the Florida Panthers 8-1 in Game 4 for their first win of the series.

title: GOTTA SEE IT: Connor McDavid Breaks Wayne Gretzky's Playoff Record With 32nd Assist
descrip: Watch as Edmonton Oilers forward Connor McDavid earns an assist on Dylan Holloway's third-period goal in Game 4 to break Wayne Gretzky's playoff record with his 32nd assist of the Stanley Cup Playoffs.

title: Darnell Nurse Scores Oilers' Fifth Goal To Chase Sergei Bobrovsky From Net
descrip: Watch as Edmonton Oilers defenceman Darnell Nurse takes a pass from Connor McDavid and finds the back of the net with a wrist shot to chase Florida Panthers goaltender Sergei Bobrovsky from the net with the fifth Oilers goal of Game 4.

title: Matthew Tkachuk Giveaway Leads To Connor McDavid Snipe On Sergei Bobrovsky
descrip: Matthew Tkachuk gives it right to the Edmonton Oilers and they capitalize on the broken play to set up Connor McDavid alone. McDavid finally solved Sergei Bobrovsky with a short side snipe.

title: GOTTA SEE IT: Dylan Holloway Uses Slick Backhand To Score Off Leon Draisaitl Feed
descrip: Watch as Leon Draisaitl gets the puck at the blue line and feeds Dylan Holloway, who uses a slick backhand toe drag to score a beauty goal and extend the Oilers' lead in the first period.

title: Vladimir Tarasenko Tips In Shot From Gustav Forsling To Put Panthers On Board
descrip: Watch as Florida Panthers' Vladimir Tarasenko displays great hand-eye with a nice tip to cut the deficit against the Oilers.

title: Mattias Janmark Shows Up Again To Feed Adam Henrique's Gritty Goal
descrip: Watch as the Edmonton Oilers get some production from their third line in Game 4 of the Stanley Cup Final, as Mattias Janmark works the puck in and finds Adam Henrique in the slot to beat Florida Panthers goalie Sergei Bobrovsky.

title: Esa Lindell Pots Slick Feed From Jason Robertson For Another Finn Goal
descrip: Watch as Dallas Stars' Esa Lindell puts home the pass from Jason Robertson for another goal by a Finnish player in the Global Series.

title: Reinhart Fires Bullet Past Oettinger For His 3rd Shorty Of The Season
descrip: Check this out, as Panthers forward Sam Reinhart holds and fires past Jake Oettinger, adding to their NHL Global Series lead vs. the Dallas Stars, with his 3rd short-handed marker of the season.

title: Panthers' Barkov Pumps Up Finnish Home Town Fans With Global Series Snipe Vs. Stars
descrip: Check this out, as Tampere, Finland native Aleksander Barkov gets his home town fans out of their seats by sniping top corner, and putting the Panthers up 2-0 over the Stars at NHL Global Series Finland.

title: NHL Players Name Their Biggest Childhood Fears 😱
descrip: From sharks to spiders, NHL players had all sorts of childhood fears and some stranger then others. What was your childhood fear? Let us know in the comments below!

title: Panthers' Evan Rodrigues Strikes 28 Seconds Into Global Series Finland

descrip: Watch NHL Games Live 🇨🇦

title: The McDavid-less Oilers | 32 Thoughts

title: NHL Highlights | Blackhawks vs. Sharks - October 31, 2024
descrip: Will Smith scored twice for the first two goals of his NHL career to lead the San Jose Sharks to a 3-2 win over the Chicago Blackhawks.

title: NHL Highlights | Oilers vs. Predators - October 31, 2024
descrip: Leon Draisaitl scored twice and Calvin Pickard made 26 saves as the Edmonton Oilers rolled to a 5-1 win over the Nashville Predators.

title: Oilers' Vasily Podkolzin Drops Jeremy Lauzon With Three BOMBS
descrip: Watch as Edmonton Oilers forward Vasily Podkolzin shows off some incredible mitts, dropping the gloves with Nashville Predators defenceman Jeremy Lauzon and blasting him with three huge punches to end the fight quickly.

title: Oilers' Zach Hyman Ends 10-Game Scoreless Drought With Breakaway Goal
descrip: Watch as Darnell Nurse sets up Zach Hyman for the breakaway, who keeps it simple and scores to end his 10-game scoreless drought to start the season.

title: NHL Highlights | Canadiens vs. Capitals - October 31, 2024
descrip: Alexander Ovechkin scored his 858th career goal and added two assists and his linemate Aliaksei Protas chipped in with a goal and an assist as the Washington Capitals defeated the Montreal Canadiens 6-3.

title: NHL Highlights | Ducks vs. Penguins - October 31, 2024
descrip: Alex Nedeljkovic made 22 saves, Sidney Crosby scored both goals, including the overtime winner, and the Pittsburgh Penguins topped the Anaheim Ducks 2-1.

descrip: The Carolina Hurricanes dominate the Boston Bruins scoring three goals in under a minute in the first period as Jack Roslovic and Andrei Svechnikov notch two goals apiece to give the Bruins their second loss in a row.

title: NHL Highlights | Maple Leafs vs. Kraken - October 31, 2024
descrip: William Nylander notches his Maple Leafs-leading seventh and eighth goals of the season helping the Toronto Maple Leafs to a 4-1 win over the Seattle Kraken.

title: NHL Highlights | Flyers vs. Blues - October 31, 2024
descrip: Bobby Brink nets the winner late in the third period after Garnet Hathaway opened the scoring off an impressive assist by Ryan Poehling to lift the Philadelphia Flyers over the St. Louis Blues for the Flyers' third win in four games.

title: Oilers' Leon Draisaitl Goes Top Shelf For A Breakaway Beauty
descrip: Watch as Edmonton Oilers star Leon Draisaitl remains red hot to start the season, breaking out and roofing one past Nashville Predators goalie Juuse Saros for a gorgeous goal.

title: Cole Caufield Stays Hot, Takes It Himself For Fourth Goal In Four Games
descrip: Watch as Cole Caufield picks the puck up in his own zone and takes it himself to score his fourth goal in four games, reaching the 10-goal milestone in the process.

title: Viktor Arvidsson Scores His First As An Oiler Off Of Draisaitl's Feed
descrip: Watch as the Edmonton Oilers pour on the pressure early against the Nashville Predators, as Leon Draisaitl sets up a perfect tap-in for Viktor Arvidsson to net him his first goal as an Oiler.

title: Hurricanes Blitz The Bruins For Three Goals In Under A Minute
descrip: Watch as the Carolina Hurricanes dominate the Boston Bruins in the first period, as Shayne Gostisbehere, Dmitry Orlov, and Martin Necas all pot goals in the span of less than a minute to blow the game open.

title: NHL Highlights | Blue Jackets vs. Capitals - November 2, 2024
descrip: Connor McMichael scored twice and Logan Thompson made 34 saves as the Washington Capitals blew out the Columbus Blue Jackets 7-2.

title: NHL Highlights | Blackhawks vs. Kings - November 2, 2024
descrip: Tyler Bertuzzi fired home the game-tying goal to cap off a huge third-period rally and Ryan Donato potted the shootout winner as the Chicago Blackhawks defeated the Los Angeles Kings 4-3.

title: Chicago Blackhawks at Los Angeles Kings | FULL Shootout Highlights - November 2, 2024
descrip: Watch the full shootout highlights between the Chicago Blackhawks and the Los Angeles Kings from November 2, 2024.

title: Tyler Bertuzzi Ties It For The Blackhawks With The Net Empty
descrip: Watch as the Chicago Blackhawks come up clutch in the final minute, as Tyler Bertuzzi's redirection hits the post and gets past Los Angeles Kings goalie Darcy Kuemper to tie it up.

title: Capitals' Alex Ovechkin, Nic Dowd Find Back Of The Net For Two Goals In 24 Seconds
descrip: Watch as Alex Ovechkin hits his patented one-timer to score his 859th career goal, followed by a sweet two-on-one rush that sees Nic Dowd net the Capitals' second goal in just 24 seconds.

title: Juraj Slafkovsky Returns To Where His NHL Journey Started
descrip: Montreal Canadiens superstar Juraj Slafkovsky met with Elliotte Friedman this past offseason in his hometown of Kosice, Slovakia to reflect on his NHL journey and visualize bringing the Stanley Cup back to his childhood home.

title: NHL Highlights | Bruins vs. Flyers - November 2, 2024
descrip: Joonas Korpisalo saved all 20 shots he faced, Matthew Poitras scored the game-winning goal and Brad Marchand tallied two points as the Boston Bruins shut out the Philadelphia Flyers 3-0.

title: NHL Highlights | Stars vs. Panthers - November 2, 2024
descrip: A.J. Greer netted a go-ahead marker, and Spencer Knight stopped 23 shots to help the Florida Panthers wrap up the Global Series in Finland with a 4-2 win against the Dallas Stars.

title: A.J. Greer Scores After Panthers Execute Play Off The Draw To Perfection
descrip: Watch as Florida Panthers forward A.J. Greer scores his first goal of the season, thanks to a slick play off the faceoff to help put his team back in front against the Dallas Stars in Tampere, Finland.

title: Stars Even Up With Goals From Evgenii Dadonov, Matt Duchene 34 Seconds Apart
descrip: Watch as Dallas Stars' Evgenii Dadonov and Matt Duchene strike quickly to even the score against the Panthers in the Global Series Finland.

title: NHL Highlights | Flames vs. Devils - November 1, 2024
descrip: The Calgary Flames welcomed Jacob Markstrom back to Alberta with a shutout win for Dan Vladar in a close fought battle. Final score 3-0.

title: Flames' Coleman And Huberdeau Bury Back-To-Back Goals 28 Seconds Apart
descrip: Watch as Calgary Flames forwards, Blake Coleman and Jonathan Huberdeau score key back-to-back third period goals just 28 seconds apart, giving them two goal cushion.

title: NHL Highlights | Lightning vs. Wild - November 1, 2024
descrip: Kirill Kaprizov added to his league leading point total with two goals and an assist, while Filip Gustavsson made 27 saves to help lead the Minnesota Wild past the Tampa Bay Lightning 5-3.

title: Confusion Ensues As Two Pucks End Up In Play In Minnesota
descrip: Watch as Kirill Kaprizov's point-blank shot flies over top of the goal, and moments later Marco Rossi misses on a breakaway but finds a puck behind the net to score as two pucks end up in play in a bizarre situation between the Wild and Lightning.

title: NHL Highlights | Islanders vs. Sabres - November 1, 2024
descrip: Maxim Tsyplakov and Bo Horvat both had a goal and an assist, while Ilya Sorokin made 32 saves to lead the New York Islanders past the Buffalo Sabres 4-3.

title: NHL Highlights | Jets vs. Blue Jackets - November 1, 2024
descrip: Nikolaj Ehlers potted his fifth career hat trick, while Josh Morrissey added a goal and an assist to help the Winnipeg Jets take care of the Columbus Blue Jackets 6-2.

title: NHL Highlights | Senators vs. Rangers - November 1, 2024
descrip: Igor Shesterkin was exceptional, making 40 saves on 41 shots, and Alexis Lafreniere had a goal and an assist to help the New York Rangers beat the Ottawa Senators 2-1.

title: Flames Present Mikael Backlund With Silver Stick In Honour Of 1,000 Games
descrip: Watch as the Calgary Flames present their captain Mikael Backlund with a silver stick, along with a framed jersey and a video presentation that featured past and present teammates, in honour of playing 1.000 NHL games.

title: Mike Reilly Exits After Scary Hit From Jordan Greenway
descrip: Jordan Greenway landed a huge hit on Mike Reilly and he appeared to hit his head on the ice after the hit. Reilly was helped off the ice and got a standing ovation from the crowd.

title: Jets' Nikolaj Ehlers Records Fifth Career Hat Trick vs. Blue Jackets
descrip: Watch as Winnipeg Jets forward Nikolaj Ehlers scores three goal to record his fifth career hat trick against the Columbus Blue Jackets.

descrip: Watch as New York Islanders forward Maxim Tsyplakov goes end-to-end with a shifty move to cut into the slot before finishing it five-hole on Devon Levi.

title: NHL Highlights | Lightning vs. Jets - November 3, 2024
